            <span>6+ patents in machine learning for semiconductor manufacturing</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Publications in top-tier journals including Neural Networks and Acta Materialia</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Active collaboration with leading Dutch universities</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>

    <!-- Download Button (Bottom) -->
    <div class="text-center pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
      <Button href="/pdfs/Tiago_Botari_CV.pdf" variant="primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
        </svg>
        Download Full CV (PDF)
      </Button>
    </div>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
